:::Bluestreak/Andromeda:::

::Bluestreak was amazed.  He had never talked with anybody this long.  He and 
Andromeda had been talking for hours upon hours about this and that, and it 
was getting late::
Andromeda:(yawns) im tired.  Walk me to my quarters?
Bluestreak: Sure
::They walk, hand in hand, to Andromeda's quarters::
Andromeda: See you in the morning.
::She kissed him.  Bluestreak felt an exteme happyness deep down in his 
spark.  They realized they didnt want to see each other in the morning.  They 
wanted to be together.  They walked into Andromeda's quarters, still kissing. 
 With one hand free from holding Andromeda, Bluestreak closed the door and 
turned out the lights::
